## Key Lessons (Session-to-Date)

1. **Tight stops killed early returns** — switching from 1.5-3% to 10% was the most impactful change
2. **Take-profits are harmful** in trending markets — STRAT4's old 3% TP sold into +50% moves
3. **CUSUM > Bollinger > Z-score > momentum** for event detection
4. **Cross-instrument signals** (new STRAT3) exploit information diffusion lag
5. **Capital deployment** remains biggest drag — ~40% cash idle

